01:23:36,039 --> 01:23:36,560
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim,

1933
01:23:36,560 --> 01:23:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo kretali u proboj,

1934
01:23:38,079 --> 01:23:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] ajde,

1935
01:23:40,539 --> 01:23:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] pomolit ćemo se,

1936
01:23:42,800 --> 01:23:45,060
[SPEAKER_00] da nas malo sreća,

1937
01:23:45,060 --> 01:23:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] i Boži blagoslov drži,

1938
01:23:48,180 --> 01:23:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] i sad i on hlekne sa nama,

1939
01:23:51,680 --> 01:23:52,680
[SPEAKER_00] onako u mraku,

1940
01:23:52,680 --> 01:23:54,600
[SPEAKER_00] i upored mene,

1941
01:23:54,600 --> 01:23:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] i sad nije,

1942
01:23:55,420 --> 01:23:56,479
[SPEAKER_00] u ime oca i sine,

1943
01:23:56,479 --> 01:23:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] duha svetoga,

1944
01:23:57,340 --> 01:23:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] a on kaže,

1945
01:23:58,859 --> 01:24:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] ej, kako se to moli,

1946
01:24:00,159 --> 01:24:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] o ništa čovječe,

1947
01:24:01,140 --> 01:24:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] samo hlekni,

1948
01:24:02,079 --> 01:24:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] u sebi,

1949
01:24:04,220 --> 01:24:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] sam sebi,

1950
01:24:06,039 --> 01:24:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] molio od Boga,

1951
01:24:07,720 --> 01:24:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] oprav za ono što to sad napravio,

1952
01:24:09,579 --> 01:24:10,439
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

1953
01:24:10,439 --> 01:24:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] Boži pomozi mi,

1954
01:24:11,199 --> 01:24:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] sad ćeš ti ja učiti,

1955
01:24:13,279 --> 01:24:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] sad ćeš mi moliti,

1956
01:24:14,539 --> 01:24:14,939
[SPEAKER_00] to će nad,

1957
01:24:14,939 --> 01:24:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, paš imamo vremena sad,

1958
01:24:16,699 --> 01:24:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] da ti ja držim,

1959
01:24:18,579 --> 01:24:19,560
[SPEAKER_00] veronauku,

1960
01:24:19,560 --> 01:24:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] trih strine,

1961
01:24:20,300 --> 01:24:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali takav čudna situacija bila,

1962
01:24:22,960 --> 01:24:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] jel,

1963
01:24:23,220 --> 01:24:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] hvala Bogu,

1964
01:24:24,779 --> 01:24:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] živi i dan danas,

1965
01:24:25,880 --> 01:24:28,060
[SPEAKER_00] ali još se nije naučio moliti,

1966
01:24:28,060 --> 01:24:29,100
[SPEAKER_00] da budemo jasni,

1967
01:24:29,100 --> 01:24:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna se ni prekriže,

1968
01:24:30,399 --> 01:24:32,520
[SPEAKER_00] dobro pa ga kamera ne vata nikad,

1969
01:24:32,520 --> 01:24:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad je u tim.

1970
01:24:35,000 --> 01:24:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

1971
01:24:36,659 --> 01:24:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] di će,

1972
01:24:37,000 --> 01:24:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] s kojom rukom će krenit,

1973
01:24:38,420 --> 01:24:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] da se prekriže,

1974
01:24:40,220 --> 01:24:41,939
[SPEAKER_00] a ima i političara takvi vidi,

1975
01:24:41,939 --> 01:24:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] možete i primijetiti na televiziji,

1976
01:24:43,680 --> 01:24:44,899
[SPEAKER_00] da vide da,

1977
01:24:44,899 --> 01:24:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] neću reći,

1978
01:24:46,619 --> 01:24:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] nabraja sad,

1979
01:24:47,460 --> 01:24:50,020
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti velikani kad dođu.

1980
01:24:50,560 --> 01:24:53,399
[SPEAKER_00] znači bilo je taki čudnija anegdota.

1981
01:24:53,399 --> 01:24:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] Još jedna informacija,

1982
01:24:54,880 --> 01:24:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam se već dotekao iz sajmišta,

1983
01:24:56,760 --> 01:24:59,100
[SPEAKER_00] i moje obiteljske kuće,

1984
01:24:59,100 --> 01:25:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam koliko vam je poznato,

1985
01:25:00,819 --> 01:25:04,560
[SPEAKER_00] meni su roditelje zaklali 15.9.91. u kući,

1986
01:25:06,319 --> 01:25:06,979
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam rođen,

1987
01:25:06,979 --> 01:25:09,600
[SPEAKER_00] kad su nam uzeli taj dio sajmišta gore.

1988
01:25:09,600 --> 01:25:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] I ne samo moje roditelje,

1989
01:25:12,119 --> 01:25:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] nego su išli po kućama,

1990
01:25:13,659 --> 01:25:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi smo se toliko brzo morali povući,

1991
01:25:18,319 --> 01:25:20,100
[SPEAKER_00] kad su nas pritisnili,

1992
01:25:20,100 --> 01:25:21,199
[SPEAKER_00] neočekivano,

1993
01:25:21,199 --> 01:25:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] jer nije ni bilo minirano,

1994
01:25:23,239 --> 01:25:23,779
[SPEAKER_00] ni ništa,

1995
01:25:23,779 --> 01:25:26,439
[SPEAKER_00] oni su dobrano narho nagrnili,

1996
01:25:27,479 --> 01:25:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] nismo imali ni dovoljno ljudi,

1997
01:25:29,180 --> 01:25:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] a oružja nikakog,

1998
01:25:31,159 --> 01:25:32,479
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se suprostavili,

1999
01:25:32,479 --> 01:25:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] tako da su nam civili ostali po kućama,

2000
01:25:35,899 --> 01:25:37,779
[SPEAKER_00] jer sakrali se u podrome,

2001
01:25:37,779 --> 01:25:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ono,

2002
01:25:38,220 --> 01:25:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] tako da su praktično domaći

2003
01:25:43,260 --> 01:25:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] i vodili su ove strance,

2004
01:25:45,819 --> 01:25:49,560
[SPEAKER_00] pa su išli po kućama i življavati se

2005
01:25:49,560 --> 01:25:50,520
[SPEAKER_00] na tim starim ljudima,

2006
01:25:50,520 --> 01:25:52,279
[SPEAKER_00] kao što smo mi znali di su oni,

2007
01:25:52,279 --> 01:25:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] oni su znali di sam ja,

2008
01:25:53,619 --> 01:25:55,520
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost jeo i Sučića,

2009
01:25:55,520 --> 01:25:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] koje spominjem često,

2010
01:25:57,159 --> 01:25:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] njegove roditelje su isto ubili,

2011
01:25:59,380 --> 01:26:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdenjka Potorčića,

2012
01:26:01,300 --> 01:26:02,560
[SPEAKER_00] žena Peretvijanovca,

2013
01:26:02,560 --> 01:26:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] tati glavu ocekli,

2014
01:26:03,739 --> 01:26:05,399
[SPEAKER_00] njega smo bez glave i sahranili,

2015
01:26:05,399 --> 01:26:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] posle mirne reintegracije,

2016
01:26:07,079 --> 01:26:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] identifikacije,

2017
01:26:07,920 --> 01:26:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] sad da vam ne nabrajam sve po ulici,

2018
01:26:10,680 --> 01:26:11,560
[SPEAKER_00] kako ste skretali,

2019
01:26:11,560 --> 01:26:14,319
[SPEAKER_00] znači nisam samo ja tako loše prošao,

2020
01:26:14,319 --> 01:26:14,939
[SPEAKER_00] međutim,

2021
01:26:14,939 --> 01:26:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja mogu reći da imam u neku ruku sreće,

2022
01:26:20,880 --> 01:26:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] mir nisam,

2023
01:26:21,880 --> 01:26:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja sam svoje roditelje pronašao,

2024
01:26:26,840 --> 01:26:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] identificirao i sahranio gore na groblju i ja znam,

2025
01:26:35,279 --> 01:26:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] di ću sad zapaliti lampion,

2026
01:26:38,140 --> 01:26:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] pomoliti se,

2027
01:26:40,720 --> 01:26:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] međutim ima dosta naših mama,

2028
01:26:43,720 --> 01:26:44,399
[SPEAKER_00] što ja kažem,

2029
01:26:44,399 --> 01:26:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] mojih mama,

2030
01:26:45,140 --> 01:26:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] mojih tata,

2031
01:26:45,960 --> 01:26:47,859
[SPEAKER_00] moje djece,

2032
01:26:47,859 --> 01:26:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] koje još uvek ne znaju,

2033
01:26:49,600 --> 01:26:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] di su njihovi najmili.

2034
01:26:53,239 --> 01:26:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] recimo i baka Šovaljička,

2035
01:26:55,840 --> 01:26:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] ona još dva sina,

2036
01:26:58,199 --> 01:26:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] nema ih nigde,

2037
01:26:59,380 --> 01:27:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] umrla je, ne zna.

2038
01:27:01,380 --> 01:27:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

2039
01:27:01,859 --> 01:27:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] znate za starog ovog Živkovića,

2040
01:27:06,140 --> 01:27:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] čiji je sin,

2041
01:27:08,119 --> 01:27:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] jedan poginio u onom An-2 avionu kod otoka,

2042
01:27:12,539 --> 01:27:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] što smo izvali poljoprivredno borbena avijacija,

2043
01:27:16,039 --> 01:27:16,279
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

2044
01:27:16,279 --> 01:27:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] on još jednog sina i tražio,

2045
01:27:20,460 --> 01:27:21,020
[SPEAKER_00] nažalosti,

2046
01:27:21,020 --> 01:27:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] još ga nije našao,

2047
01:27:21,699 --> 01:27:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] a umro je prije,

2048
01:27:22,680 --> 01:27:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna koliko,

2049
01:27:23,539 --> 01:27:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] možda mjese,

2050
01:27:24,180 --> 01:27:24,520
[SPEAKER_00] dana,

2051
01:27:24,520 --> 01:27:25,020
[SPEAKER_00] dva,

2052
01:27:25,020 --> 01:27:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako je stari Živkovića,

2053
01:27:27,000 --> 01:27:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] ostati jedino na svim tim snimkama,

2054
01:27:29,600 --> 01:27:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] da je Rodaga digona leđa na sebi,

2055
01:27:33,380 --> 01:27:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] i da je Čekićem razbio onu čiriličnu ploču na milici,

2056
01:27:37,340 --> 01:27:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] na policiji,

2057
01:27:38,680 --> 01:27:41,600
[SPEAKER_00] to je srpsko-hrvatska milicija kod nas još uvek.

2058
01:27:41,600 --> 01:27:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] Potom će ostati poznata i Čekić je sačuvo,

2059
01:27:45,079 --> 01:27:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] kod njega je kući baka ga čuva.

2060
01:27:46,800 --> 01:27:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, on još jednog sina tražio,

2061
01:27:50,260 --> 01:27:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] i vrijeme prolazi,

2062
01:27:51,420 --> 01:27:53,899
[SPEAKER_00] ti stari lagano umiru,

2063
01:27:53,899 --> 01:27:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] zato ja kažem da sam imao više sreće od njih,

2064
01:27:57,239 --> 01:28:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ja ipak svoje roditelje pronašao,

2065
01:28:01,220 --> 01:28:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] identificirao i da znam da ću se pomoliti.

2066
01:28:04,500 --> 01:28:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi volio da vi mene nešto pitate,

2067
01:28:10,539 --> 01:28:13,979
[SPEAKER_00] ja sad ovako možda i nevezano pričam,

2068
01:28:13,979 --> 01:28:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali imam ja dosta toga za reć,

2069
01:28:17,000 --> 01:28:20,060
[SPEAKER_00] ali poticaj bi bio i kad bi vi mene

2070
01:28:20,060 --> 01:28:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] nešto pitali, ne znam koliko ste upučeni upoznati sa situacijom,

2071
01:28:24,079 --> 01:28:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] tako da sam ja spreman i vama odgovarati na pitanje,

2072
01:28:27,039 --> 01:28:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] kako god znam sve od gubice do kako smo se snalazili.

2073
01:28:34,800 --> 01:28:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] oprosti sam mu, on je prvi digor.

2074
01:28:36,680 --> 01:28:40,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, ja, vidio sam, malo smo ovoga vrijeme prekad dašili,

2075
01:28:40,260 --> 01:28:43,279
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo ja ću postaviti samo vremena za jedno pitanje,

2076
01:28:43,279 --> 01:28:49,939
[SPEAKER_01] evo imaš tu čast, pa evo nakon toga bismo morali krenuti sa daljnim predavanjima.

2077
01:28:50,020 --> 01:28:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte ići, ovde vam je Hrvatska pravo, a ne naša krajina je ona.

2078
01:28:59,800 --> 01:29:06,359
[SPEAKER_02] evo, moj ime Antonio i moje tata bio isto u ratu i zapravo želim pitat,

2079
01:29:06,359 --> 01:29:11,140
[SPEAKER_02] znam da je Štuka bio najveći zločinac na ovčari,

2080
01:29:11,140 --> 01:29:17,520
[SPEAKER_02] šta je s njim završio, mislim da je zapravo slobođena na Beograskom sudu

2081
01:29:17,520 --> 01:29:21,619
[SPEAKER_02] i zapravo malo sam dečke proveo u petak po gradu

2082
01:29:21,619 --> 01:29:23,800
[SPEAKER_02] i pokazao sam neke stvari koje i ja znam u gradu,

2083
01:29:23,800 --> 01:29:26,779
[SPEAKER_02] a zapravo ne znam toliko puno, ali znam puno više od ostalih,

2084
01:29:26,779 --> 01:29:28,000
[SPEAKER_02] jer me to jako zanimalo.

2085
01:29:28,000 --> 01:29:34,779
[SPEAKER_02] Koji je bio omjer Srba koji je učestvao u borbama za Vukovar

2086
01:29:34,779 --> 01:29:38,880
[SPEAKER_02] i koji je to omjer bio u vojnom dijelu?

2087
01:29:38,880 --> 01:29:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako, najtočnije podatke tima Ante nazor.

2088
01:29:47,520 --> 01:29:51,800
[SPEAKER_00] On je čisto, ono, povijesno, činjenično.

2089
01:29:51,800 --> 01:29:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] On zna da je naz bilo tu 1803,

2090
01:29:55,039 --> 01:30:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] a odvana, što on broji regularni vojni snaga oko 30.000,

2091
01:30:02,420 --> 01:30:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] a negde do 45.000 se rasteže sa tim rezernim i dobrovoljcima,

2092
01:30:09,819 --> 01:30:13,859
[SPEAKER_00] tu su bili i Jarkanovi, i Šešeljevi, i Beli Orlovi,

2093
01:30:13,859 --> 01:30:17,560
[SPEAKER_00] i Charlie Chaplin i neki pop te pita, kinezovi, neki ljudi.

2094
01:30:17,560 --> 01:30:21,840
[SPEAKER_00] Malte ne svaka mjesna zajednica po Srbiji je dobrovoljce slala ovde.

2095
01:30:21,840 --> 01:30:25,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je ko prošlo, znaš, i Niška specijalna,

2096
01:30:25,279 --> 01:30:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] i kod nas je ovde na teren su došle tri oklopne brigade,

2097
01:30:32,140 --> 01:30:36,140
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno korpusa, ne brigade, korpus.

2098
01:30:37,140 --> 01:30:40,560
[SPEAKER_00] Novosadski tenkovski korpus, Banjalučki tenkovski korpus

2099
01:30:40,560 --> 01:30:43,600
[SPEAKER_00] i eletna oklopna gardijska brigada iz Beograda.

2100
01:30:43,600 --> 01:30:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su svi imali 80 tvorke i to nove.

2101
01:30:49,020 --> 01:30:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan od njihove velikana je bacio kašiku ovdje.

2102
01:30:52,840 --> 01:30:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] Komadant Novosadskog tenkovskog korpusa.

2103
01:30:57,340 --> 01:30:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] To možete nas sad na internetu.

2104
01:30:59,699 --> 01:31:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] Opisuje se kao jedan od viđenijih generala,

2105
01:31:02,920 --> 01:31:06,359
[SPEAKER_00] koji je među svojim suborcima, tenkistima,

2106
01:31:06,359 --> 01:31:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] poginio u akciji oslobađanja Vukovara.

2107
01:31:11,100 --> 01:31:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je blago je Bratić ili ne znam,

2108
01:31:14,800 --> 01:31:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] nekao Bratić mu je prezima, ali ne, nije bitno,

2109
01:31:18,880 --> 01:31:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali Bratić, general, komadant Novosadskog tenkovskog korpusa.

2110
01:31:23,119 --> 01:31:27,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas je mali jasre, pošto je on bio magista ratni vještina,

2111
01:31:27,819 --> 01:31:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] onda je on tražio da mi džepamo ove smradove,

2112
01:31:34,180 --> 01:31:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] da mu donosimo knjižice.

2113
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] jer on je u principu kod sebe tamo u štabu,

2114
01:31:39,659 --> 01:31:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] po knjižicama, po vojnim poštama,

2115
01:31:42,119 --> 01:31:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] on je to sve slago,

2116
01:31:44,119 --> 01:31:47,560
[SPEAKER_00] pa je znao koje snage su upotrebljene na nama,

2117
01:31:47,560 --> 01:31:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno koje snage su upotrebljavale,

2118
01:31:49,460 --> 01:31:53,060
[SPEAKER_00] pa je mogo pretpostaviti zašto će biti namjenjene te snage.

2119
01:31:53,060 --> 01:31:57,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, ja, brzo potezne, lakojurušne, motorizirane,

2120
01:31:57,020 --> 01:32:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] pješačke snage, ne znam, nije ove, one,

2121
01:32:00,380 --> 01:32:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] zrakoplovstvo, da ne kažem,

2122
01:32:02,840 --> 01:32:06,100
[SPEAKER_00] i sa brodova, sa Dunava,

2123
01:32:06,100 --> 01:32:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] oni patrolni brodovi od Jenova,

2124
01:32:08,539 --> 01:32:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] tako da on sebi neku sliku stvaro oko toga.

2125
01:32:11,739 --> 01:32:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad se dolazi na veče,

2126
01:32:14,000 --> 01:32:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] po noći kod njih agregat imaju promenit bateriju,

2127
01:32:17,220 --> 01:32:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] uzeti novu, punu bateriju,

2128
01:32:18,539 --> 01:32:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] išli na položaj,

2129
01:32:19,159 --> 01:32:22,939
[SPEAKER_00] i onda iz džepova vadiš knjižice koliko si uspio skupiti,

2130
01:32:22,939 --> 01:32:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] povadiš to, pobacaš mu nastol,

2131
01:32:25,079 --> 01:32:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] onda on otvara,

2132
01:32:25,819 --> 01:32:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] a, dobro,

2133
01:32:28,359 --> 01:32:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj ide tu,

2134
01:32:29,380 --> 01:32:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj ide tu,

2135
01:32:31,300 --> 01:32:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] ova knjižica ovde,

2136
01:32:32,579 --> 01:32:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] onda jednu otvorio.

2137
01:32:33,880 --> 01:32:35,859
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je ovaj?

2138
01:32:35,859 --> 01:32:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] A, svi on,

2139
01:32:37,199 --> 01:32:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali ko zna gdje,

2140
01:32:38,239 --> 01:32:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, boli na suvo,

2141
01:32:39,880 --> 01:32:40,560
[SPEAKER_00] ko je taj dži?

2142
01:32:40,560 --> 01:32:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kao znate ko je taj?

2143
01:32:42,460 --> 01:32:44,560
[SPEAKER_00] A jo, još više me zainteresirao,

2144
01:32:44,560 --> 01:32:44,979
[SPEAKER_00] ko je taj?

2145
01:32:44,979 --> 01:32:45,479
[SPEAKER_00] Šta me brige?

2146
01:32:45,479 --> 01:32:47,020
[SPEAKER_00] Bitno da je bacio kaško,

2147
01:32:47,020 --> 01:32:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] da je knjižica u tvoje rukama.

2148
01:32:48,260 --> 01:32:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, to je komatant Novosadskog tenkovskog korpusa.

2149
01:32:51,579 --> 01:32:53,819
[SPEAKER_00] Opa, to je ono bilo za nate.

2150
01:32:53,819 --> 01:32:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dobar.

2151
01:32:54,680 --> 01:32:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ali su čutali jedno dva dana,

2152
01:32:57,260 --> 01:32:59,100
[SPEAKER_00] tek su nakon dva dana objavili,

2153
01:32:59,100 --> 01:33:00,560
[SPEAKER_00] obznanili tu vijest,

2154
01:33:00,560 --> 01:33:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] i to tu se danas može naći,

2155
01:33:02,340 --> 01:33:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] TV Beograd je to obznanio.

2156
01:33:04,720 --> 01:33:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] Još jedan od velikana njihovi,

2157
01:33:07,159 --> 01:33:08,600
[SPEAKER_00] tobožni Arkan,

2158
01:33:08,600 --> 01:33:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] on je na Lužac došao,

2159
01:33:10,539 --> 01:33:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] on je svoje oklopnjake zvao isto Tigrovi,

2160
01:33:13,880 --> 01:33:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] jer se sprdoza u vreme bljeska

2161
01:33:17,739 --> 01:33:19,100
[SPEAKER_00] da ne u vreme,

2162
01:33:19,100 --> 01:33:21,100
[SPEAKER_00] nego bilo je upitno

2163
01:33:21,100 --> 01:33:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] će biti kakvih akcija na okupiranom području,

2164
01:33:25,100 --> 01:33:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] pa je on rekao,

2165
01:33:25,680 --> 01:33:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] baš bi volio da se susredne

2166
01:33:27,220 --> 01:33:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] njegovi Tigrovi sa zagrebačkim mačićima,

2167
01:33:30,319 --> 01:33:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] onako pocijenivačke,

2168
01:33:31,619 --> 01:33:32,859
[SPEAKER_00] to rekao u Erdutu,

2169
01:33:32,859 --> 01:33:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] kad je davao intervju.

2170
01:33:34,260 --> 01:33:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali taj mangup je dolio,

2171
01:33:39,500 --> 01:33:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] oni su nam upali na Lužac u jedno popovodne,

2172
01:33:43,420 --> 01:33:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] nismo imali dovoljno snaga,

2173
01:33:46,279 --> 01:33:48,239
[SPEAKER_00] međutim, organizirali smo se,

2174
01:33:48,239 --> 01:33:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] sakupili se,

2175
01:33:49,079 --> 01:33:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] pobrojali se,

2176
01:33:50,300 --> 01:33:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] dovukli još sami,

2177
01:33:53,119 --> 01:33:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] ponekoliko ljudi sa strane,

2178
01:33:55,600 --> 01:33:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] za drugi punktova,

2179
01:33:57,619 --> 01:33:59,939
[SPEAKER_00] i u dva sata ujutro smo mi krenili,

2180
01:33:59,939 --> 01:34:02,220
[SPEAKER_00] po noći smo i oterali iz Salusa na poj.

2181
01:34:02,760 --> 01:34:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, drugi dan kad su pokušali,

2182
01:34:06,500 --> 01:34:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo sve stabilizirali,

2183
01:34:08,000 --> 01:34:08,819
[SPEAKER_00] nismo mogli ući.

2184
01:34:09,819 --> 01:34:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, tada je ovaj jedan moj reko,

2185
01:34:11,760 --> 01:34:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

2186
01:34:12,699 --> 01:34:14,100
[SPEAKER_00] e, Samuraj, kaže,

2187
01:34:14,100 --> 01:34:15,520
[SPEAKER_00] pogodio sam Marka na Paoje.

2188
01:34:15,520 --> 01:34:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Uvriko, dobro,

2189
01:34:16,840 --> 01:34:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] idemo dalje.

2190
01:34:17,859 --> 01:34:19,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa to sad,

2191
01:34:19,680 --> 01:34:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] dalje nastavlja se pucinjava,

2192
01:34:21,039 --> 01:34:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] dok se to sve ne očisti i ne smiri.

2193
01:34:23,520 --> 01:34:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, oni su kasnije objavili,

2194
01:34:26,079 --> 01:34:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] je on dom.

2195
01:34:27,239 --> 01:34:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imao je sreće.

2196
01:34:30,539 --> 01:34:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] Imao je onog malog heklera,

2197
01:34:32,760 --> 01:34:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam ko pozna to oružje.

2198
01:34:34,159 --> 01:34:35,939
[SPEAKER_00] Hekler mali,

2199
01:34:35,939 --> 01:34:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] nosio je ispred sebe

2200
01:34:37,500 --> 01:34:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] i pogodio ga je u palac.

2201
01:34:40,159 --> 01:34:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] I metak je ostao u toj plastičnoj držišti.

2202
01:34:42,960 --> 01:34:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, bio povređen samo prostrijel kroz palac.

2203
01:34:47,579 --> 01:34:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] Da je, ah,

2204
01:34:52,220 --> 01:34:54,520
[SPEAKER_00] pošlo četiri centimetra gore, dole,

2205
01:34:54,520 --> 01:34:55,979
[SPEAKER_00] dobio bi u menzu

2206
01:34:55,979 --> 01:34:57,520
[SPEAKER_00] i on bi bacio kašiku.

2207
01:34:57,520 --> 01:34:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, nažalaz,

2208
01:34:59,020 --> 01:35:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] teto preživio to tu kod nas,

2209
01:35:00,699 --> 01:35:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam ga...

2210
01:35:02,699 --> 01:35:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijem se izraziti ovdje.

2211
01:35:06,159 --> 01:35:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] Bacio kašiku u Beogradu,

2212
01:35:08,640 --> 01:35:10,760
[SPEAKER_00] tamo od svojih kriminalaca i lobova.

2213
01:35:10,760 --> 01:35:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da se zna,

2214
01:35:13,680 --> 01:35:16,560
[SPEAKER_00] Antena Azor ima sigurne podatke

2215
01:35:16,560 --> 01:35:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] o svemu tome,

2216
01:35:18,319 --> 01:35:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] koliko šta i čega je

2217
01:35:20,159 --> 01:35:22,140
[SPEAKER_00] nasrtalo na nas.

2218
01:35:22,859 --> 01:35:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ima i originalnu zapoved.

2219
01:35:24,760 --> 01:35:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] Neki sa strane kažu,

2220
01:35:27,159 --> 01:35:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao u Vukovaru je počerat novinari,

2221
01:35:29,119 --> 01:35:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad pošlo pet leta,

2222
01:35:29,859 --> 01:35:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] 84 dana, 82 dana boli.

2223
01:35:34,039 --> 01:35:34,600
[SPEAKER_00] Alo,

2224
01:35:34,600 --> 01:35:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] ko ti bi dozvoljalo da brojiš dana?

2225
01:35:36,779 --> 01:35:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ko ti je dao taj podat?

2226
01:35:38,439 --> 01:35:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, oduzmi od 18. i 11. unazad.

2227
01:35:40,920 --> 01:35:44,979
[SPEAKER_00] Kad onda misliš da je po tvojom počerat u Vukovaru?

2228
01:35:44,979 --> 01:35:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] O čemu pričaš ti?

2229
01:35:45,699 --> 01:35:46,560
[SPEAKER_00] Ko ti je dao taj dat?

2230
01:35:46,560 --> 01:35:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Na čemu se bazirate?

2231
01:35:48,159 --> 01:35:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] Na JNA zapovedi,

2232
01:35:50,260 --> 01:35:55,060
[SPEAKER_00] 22.8. ili 23.,

2233
01:35:55,060 --> 01:35:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] tu negde,

2234
01:35:56,680 --> 01:35:59,399
[SPEAKER_00] u 20. u mesecu,

2235
01:35:59,399 --> 01:36:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nazor ima original zapoved,

2236
01:36:02,039 --> 01:36:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] vrhovna komanda srpske vojske u Beugradu,

2237
01:36:04,819 --> 01:36:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] donela je odluku,

2238
01:36:06,380 --> 01:36:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] pošto su već imali dobri gubitaka ovdje,

2239
01:36:08,840 --> 01:36:14,020
[SPEAKER_00] da se pitanje Vukovara reši u roku od 3 do 5 dana.

2240
01:36:14,020 --> 01:36:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] I u pasu dole piše opasa,

2241
01:36:16,779 --> 01:36:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] u ovnoj opasi piše,

2242
01:36:18,899 --> 01:36:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] bez prisustva medija.

2243
01:36:20,779 --> 01:36:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

2244
01:36:23,380 --> 01:36:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] Vukovar treba rešiti u roku od 3 do 5 dana,

2245
01:36:27,279 --> 01:36:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] originalno zapoved,

2246
01:36:28,739 --> 01:36:32,100
[SPEAKER_00] da se počne sa 24. i 8.

2247
01:36:32,100 --> 01:36:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sa svim što su navukli,

2248
01:36:34,380 --> 01:36:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] i preko Dunava,

2249
01:36:35,340 --> 01:36:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo po ovim okolnim selima,

2250
01:36:38,000 --> 01:36:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatskim selima,

2251
01:36:39,960 --> 01:36:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] pretižito naseljenim pravoslavnim stanoništvom,

2252
01:36:43,319 --> 01:36:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] koja su njima dopala u ruke,

2253
01:36:46,380 --> 01:36:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] kompletno okružili,

2254
01:36:48,819 --> 01:36:50,520
[SPEAKER_00] trebali su i zrakoplostvo,

2255
01:36:50,520 --> 01:36:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] trebalo je sve to navaliti,

2256
01:36:52,119 --> 01:36:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] i ovi brodovi sa Dunava.

2257
01:36:53,680 --> 01:36:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] Trebalo je nas pritisniti,

2258
01:36:56,100 --> 01:36:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] računali su verovatno da ćemo mi,

2259
01:36:58,159 --> 01:37:00,520
[SPEAKER_00] kao Ilok, Babska, Šarengrad,

2260
01:37:00,520 --> 01:37:02,319
[SPEAKER_00] recimo ta sela bivše općine,

2261
01:37:02,319 --> 01:37:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] Vukovar,

2262
01:37:02,859 --> 01:37:06,260
[SPEAKER_00] pokupiti prnje i negdje pokušati pobeći,

2263
01:37:06,260 --> 01:37:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo se mi povući,

2264
01:37:08,119 --> 01:37:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, prema Vinkovcima, Osijeku,

2265
01:37:09,640 --> 01:37:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo ostaviti radi.

2266
01:37:10,659 --> 01:37:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, njima se nešto tu desilo.

2267
01:37:15,060 --> 01:37:23,439
[SPEAKER_00] Doživjeli su u tom napadu Luka Andrijanić im je srušio dva aviona u tom napadu.

2268
01:37:23,439 --> 01:37:34,600
[SPEAKER_00] Srušio mi je dva aviona,

2269
01:37:34,600 --> 01:37:36,020
[SPEAKER_00] ovi sa trpinske ceste,

2270
01:37:36,020 --> 01:37:36,899
[SPEAKER_00] na njej krenilo

2271
01:37:36,899 --> 01:37:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] otprilike 50-ak tenkova.

2272
01:37:39,279 --> 01:37:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] I to u dva, tri reda.

2273
01:37:41,159 --> 01:37:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjeli se koliko je ono širok šor kod nas,

2274
01:37:43,300 --> 01:37:44,479
[SPEAKER_00] gdje su kuće u razmaku.

2275
01:37:45,020 --> 01:37:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] i jedni pucaju levo, jedni desno.

2276
01:37:47,159 --> 01:37:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] Udaraju i redom, ruše kuću po kuću, jel?

2277
01:37:49,600 --> 01:37:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] Praktično.

2278
01:37:50,500 --> 01:37:52,979
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo su i dečki sačekali,

2279
01:37:52,979 --> 01:37:54,859
[SPEAKER_00] devet tenkova je uništeno tad.

2280
01:37:54,859 --> 01:38:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] I u tom vršljanju oni ostali su se povukli

2281
01:38:01,340 --> 01:38:06,680
[SPEAKER_00] i na toj strani je negdje oko 600 vojnika pješaka bacilo u Kašiku.

2282
01:38:06,680 --> 01:38:11,520
[SPEAKER_00] To vršljanje je trajalo negdje oko svojih 4,5 sata.

2283
01:38:11,520 --> 01:38:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] A na samoj trpinskoj cesti tada je bilo,

2284
01:38:15,020 --> 01:38:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] 47 momaka.

2285
01:38:16,460 --> 01:38:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] 47 momaka.

2286
01:38:18,619 --> 01:38:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sad nas ima tu okoliko.

2287
01:38:20,579 --> 01:38:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bili bi jaka snaga da smo bili tamo u to vrijeme.

2288
01:38:25,619 --> 01:38:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ranjeno je 11 civila od tog granatiranja po gradu,

2289
01:38:31,800 --> 01:38:34,560
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje i po borovu naselju.

2290
01:38:34,560 --> 01:38:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] Niko nije poginio.

2291
01:38:36,180 --> 01:38:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] Od nas niko nije bio ranjen.

2292
01:38:37,619 --> 01:38:40,060
[SPEAKER_00] Mi, mečustavno, kad smo se sastali,

2293
01:38:40,060 --> 01:38:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad je to zatiše, svi su bili bledi zeleni.

2294
01:38:43,159 --> 01:38:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam sebe nisam vidio, verovatno da sam bio i ja tako i da su mi kolena,

2295
01:38:46,539 --> 01:38:48,479
[SPEAKER_00] su mi sigurno klecela po i svima ostalima.

2296
01:38:48,479 --> 01:38:53,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nas je onda neka kuvatila, neka huja.

2297
01:38:53,439 --> 01:38:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, to je to, ubili smo, jona, gotovo, vrati, gotovo.

2298
01:38:57,260 --> 01:39:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, sad smo mi, dobiješ, ono malo, poleta dobiješ nekomu.

2299
01:39:02,539 --> 01:39:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, oni su mirovali jedno, dva dana,

2300
01:39:05,260 --> 01:39:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je teško zatišen, bez metka.

2301
01:39:07,619 --> 01:39:14,100
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su kasnije kretali sve jače, sve jače, sve jače i sve više.

2302
01:39:14,100 --> 01:39:20,600
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da smo, eto, doživili i taj naš slom obrane same.

2303
01:39:20,600 --> 01:39:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] Za nas su bili svi dani jednako teški.

2304
01:39:30,300 --> 01:39:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] Za nekog sa strane mogu reći, ali ne sme ni priča šta je nama bilo teško

2305
01:39:36,420 --> 01:39:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] i nama određiva dane koji su nam bili najtežki.

2306
01:39:38,680 --> 01:39:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] Mi sami možemo, svako osobno ima nekakav dan,

2307
01:39:42,600 --> 01:39:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] da se razumemo, koji mu je najtežki.

2308
01:39:45,439 --> 01:39:50,680
[SPEAKER_00] Posobno neko dijelovi mogu reći, ne znam, u tom periodu da im je bilo najtežo.

2309
01:39:50,680 --> 01:39:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sa strane niko ne može reći, e, već ste, taj dan vama bio onako,

2310
01:39:57,039 --> 01:39:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] možda kad si ti gledao iz Hrvatske dole,

2311
01:39:59,960 --> 01:40:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] onda je tebi bilo teško gledati na televiziju,

2312
01:40:03,500 --> 01:40:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali meni je svaki dan bio težak i noć svaka mi je bila težka.

2313
01:40:06,800 --> 01:40:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, o težini i osjećaju osobno to prepuštan svakome.

2314
01:40:12,600 --> 01:40:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] A taktički sada i, ne znam, nija,

2315
01:40:15,579 --> 01:40:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je upita i od nekih stručnjaka,

2316
01:40:20,079 --> 01:40:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji su nam dolazili iz MP RAJ,

2317
01:40:22,579 --> 01:40:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] iz američkih vojni snaga,

2318
01:40:24,680 --> 01:40:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] oni iz Koreje, iz Vijetnama,

2319
01:40:26,180 --> 01:40:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] ti dosluženi njihovi pukovnici,

2320
01:40:29,079 --> 01:40:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] vaki, naki,

2321
01:40:29,720 --> 01:40:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] pa kad te pitaju

2322
01:40:31,239 --> 01:40:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] kakvu taktiku se upotrebljavali,

2323
01:40:34,859 --> 01:40:37,100
[SPEAKER_00] kakvu strategiju se upotrebljavali,

2324
01:40:37,100 --> 01:40:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] gledam u nje,

2325
01:40:37,880 --> 01:40:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja nam tri minute vojne škole,

2326
01:40:39,680 --> 01:40:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] alo, kakva taktika,

2327
01:40:42,600 --> 01:40:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] pucaj, vrišti, plaći i beši ako si promaši,

2328
01:40:45,699 --> 01:40:48,020
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi, vrati se nazad i ponovo pucaj.

2329
01:40:48,020 --> 01:40:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kaka ti je to tako?

2330
01:40:49,880 --> 01:40:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] O čem ti priča?

2331
01:40:51,579 --> 01:41:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam.

2332
01:41:01,739 --> 01:41:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si imao neko pitanje?

2333
01:41:06,159 --> 01:41:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ne smiješ?

2334
01:41:07,840 --> 01:41:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ili više ne smiješ pitanje?

2335
01:41:09,420 --> 01:41:11,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, možda samo da ovo što si ti rekao,

2336
01:41:11,560 --> 01:41:13,319
[UNKNOWN] objasni kako je dobio nadimak samuraj.

2337
01:41:13,319 --> 01:41:14,220
[SPEAKER_01] A samuraj?

2338
01:41:14,220 --> 01:41:15,180
[SPEAKER_01] To si bio najavio,

2339
01:41:15,180 --> 01:41:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] a nije ovaj...

2340
01:41:16,000 --> 01:41:16,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

2341
01:41:16,159 --> 01:41:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] To će biti i ovoga, spoiler ovoga...

2342
01:41:18,920 --> 01:41:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] Što se tiče toga,

2343
01:41:20,859 --> 01:41:22,779
[SPEAKER_00] kod nas je svako dobio neki nadimak.

2344
01:41:22,779 --> 01:41:24,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ko je došao sa strane,

2345
01:41:24,439 --> 01:41:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili mi međusobno.

2346
01:41:25,380 --> 01:41:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas je bilo i crni,

2347
01:41:27,159 --> 01:41:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] i žuti,

2348
01:41:27,800 --> 01:41:28,560
[SPEAKER_00] i crveni,

2349
01:41:28,560 --> 01:41:29,260
[SPEAKER_00] i plavi,

2350
01:41:29,260 --> 01:41:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] i zeleni,

2351
01:41:30,460 --> 01:41:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] i lavovi,

2352
01:41:31,239 --> 01:41:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] i grabovi,

2353
01:41:31,960 --> 01:41:32,560
[SPEAKER_00] i ševe,

2354
01:41:32,560 --> 01:41:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] i šljuke,

2355
01:41:33,260 --> 01:41:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] i rode.

2356
01:41:34,840 --> 01:41:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Svako se nekako zvalo.

2357
01:41:37,039 --> 01:41:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] Čak recimo ovi,

2358
01:41:38,380 --> 01:41:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] od Damjana,

2359
01:41:41,140 --> 01:41:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost pokojnog sa sajmišta,

2360
01:41:43,340 --> 01:41:45,600
[SPEAKER_00] on je bio nekako najkrupniji,

2361
01:41:45,600 --> 01:41:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] najjači.

2362
01:41:46,260 --> 01:41:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pa uvijek je u onim šalama

2363
01:41:49,159 --> 01:41:50,720
[SPEAKER_00] prijašnjim bilo ono pupčina.

2364
01:41:50,720 --> 01:41:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Neće kada se ljubavni žulj,

2365
01:41:52,699 --> 01:41:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] nego tomu je bojler kao.

2366
01:41:54,300 --> 01:41:56,319
[SPEAKER_00] Onda jedan malo manji,

2367
01:41:56,319 --> 01:41:57,640
[SPEAKER_00] pa još manji pupčina.

2368
01:41:57,640 --> 01:42:00,180
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako je dobio on nadimak bojler?

2369
01:42:00,180 --> 01:42:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda je bio on veliki bojler,

2370
01:42:02,680 --> 01:42:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] pa srednji bojler,

2371
01:42:04,260 --> 01:42:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] pa mali bojler,

2372
01:42:05,260 --> 01:42:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] pa smo ovog jednog mlađeg dečka

2373
01:42:07,760 --> 01:42:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] nazvali bojlerčić.

2374
01:42:08,880 --> 01:42:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, četiri bojlera su to bila.

2375
01:42:11,079 --> 01:42:14,199
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ja recimo,

2376
01:42:14,199 --> 01:42:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] pošto sam majstor,

2377
01:42:15,399 --> 01:42:17,399
[SPEAKER_00] bio je za to hladno na oružanje

2378
01:42:17,399 --> 01:42:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] i volio sam,

2379
01:42:18,680 --> 01:42:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, žena me natrala

2380
01:42:20,140 --> 01:42:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] da kupim fotoaparat,

2381
01:42:21,279 --> 01:42:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] imao sam smenu osam,

2382
01:42:22,399 --> 01:42:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa gdje god sam išao u muzeje,

2383
01:42:24,460 --> 01:42:27,319
[SPEAKER_00] volio sam uslikati u vitrinama

2384
01:42:27,319 --> 01:42:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] i što se tiče kugura

2385
01:42:29,579 --> 01:42:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] i koje čega,

2386
01:42:30,220 --> 01:42:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali noževi, bodeži, sablje,

2387
01:42:31,960 --> 01:42:32,439
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ono,

2388
01:42:32,439 --> 01:42:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam to kovu.

2389
01:42:34,180 --> 01:42:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] Uradio oni sam,

2390
01:42:36,619 --> 01:42:39,560
[SPEAKER_00] pokušavao sam dostići te stare majstore,

2391
01:42:39,560 --> 01:42:42,340
[SPEAKER_00] prema da se njih nikad ne može dostići,

2392
01:42:42,340 --> 01:42:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] oni imaju svoje tajne.

2393
01:42:43,420 --> 01:42:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali više me interesirala ta strana,

2394
01:42:45,859 --> 01:42:48,220
[SPEAKER_00] gore istok, Japan,

2395
01:42:48,220 --> 01:42:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] i ta kultura,

2396
01:42:49,260 --> 01:42:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] i taj kodeks časti,

2397
01:42:51,079 --> 01:42:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] taj dio njihov moralni,

2398
01:42:54,840 --> 01:42:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali i sablje i noževi,

2399
01:42:57,340 --> 01:42:59,220
[SPEAKER_00] mačevi njihovi su me interesirali,

2400
01:42:59,220 --> 01:43:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] zato što jedini se koriste sa dvema rukama,

2401
01:43:02,800 --> 01:43:06,180
[SPEAKER_00] nose sablju na pačke sa oštricom prema gore,

2402
01:43:06,180 --> 01:43:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] na poseban način se vadi,

2403
01:43:07,960 --> 01:43:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosu na evropske,

2404
01:43:09,239 --> 01:43:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] španjolska, francuska,

2405
01:43:10,359 --> 01:43:11,859
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje imaju florete,

2406
01:43:11,859 --> 01:43:12,779
[SPEAKER_00] one šitskalice,

2407
01:43:12,779 --> 01:43:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] di imaju jatagane na turskoj strani i krivošije,

2408
01:43:16,739 --> 01:43:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] di vinkinzi imaju svoje ravne mačeve,

2409
01:43:19,939 --> 01:43:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje vitezovi po Evropi imaju one halebarde i koje šta drugo,

2410
01:43:25,199 --> 01:43:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] mene je više ovo vuklo.

2411
01:43:26,319 --> 01:43:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sam si ja pred sam rad iskovo i katanu,

2412
01:43:31,159 --> 01:43:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] to je dugački mač,

2413
01:43:32,600 --> 01:43:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] vakizaši kao kratki mač,

2414
01:43:34,880 --> 01:43:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] i tanto nož.

2415
01:43:37,279 --> 01:43:44,399
[SPEAKER_00] I sad u tom našem uzburkanom vremenu,

2416
01:43:44,399 --> 01:43:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] nekome, tata sačuvo možda bajonet,

2417
01:43:47,199 --> 01:43:50,979
[SPEAKER_00] za M908, M408, kriomice čuvo ga je,

2418
01:43:50,979 --> 01:43:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] ali sad je došao red da i on obesi nekaki nož,

2419
01:43:54,399 --> 01:43:55,899
[SPEAKER_00] pa da ima bajonet,

2420
01:43:55,899 --> 01:43:57,300
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, u tim militanti stvari,

2421
01:43:57,300 --> 01:43:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] neki su nosili lovačke noževe,

2422
01:43:59,300 --> 01:44:02,159
[SPEAKER_00] neko nije imao nož, recimo, jel?

2423
01:44:02,159 --> 01:44:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] Neko je nosio nož od kalašnikova koji je oteo,

2424
01:44:05,340 --> 01:44:08,520
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi nismo dobivali sa bajonetama, jel?

2425
01:44:08,520 --> 01:44:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] Te kalašnikova,

2426
01:44:09,760 --> 01:44:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali kod nekog kretena je našo pa sebi prikačao,

2427
01:44:12,859 --> 01:44:14,399
[SPEAKER_00] skinio sam njega, sebi prikačao.

2428
01:44:14,399 --> 01:44:16,020
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ja sam ovaj,

2429
01:44:16,020 --> 01:44:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] nož, nož, uzet ću ja moj nož,

2430
01:44:20,899 --> 01:44:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] koji sam ja iskovo.

2431
01:44:23,600 --> 01:44:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] Tanto nož,

2432
01:44:24,659 --> 01:44:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] klasično, ona čista japanske oštrica, sve je ok.

2433
01:44:28,619 --> 01:44:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] I držao sam ga za pojasom,

2434
01:44:30,699 --> 01:44:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] zavezanim.

2435
01:44:31,659 --> 01:44:33,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je tako malo virilo,

2436
01:44:33,460 --> 01:44:35,520
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

2437
01:44:35,520 --> 01:44:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] Držka je za šaku i po.

2438
01:44:38,039 --> 01:44:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] dosta velika držka u odnosu na samu oštricu.

2439
01:44:41,640 --> 01:44:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] I tako kakav sam bio u gradu,

2440
01:44:46,319 --> 01:44:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] dobio sam nadimak, samoraj.

2441
01:44:50,000 --> 01:44:51,159
[SPEAKER_00] zbog tog noža.

2442
01:44:51,159 --> 01:44:55,560
[SPEAKER_00] Odatle mi nadima,

2443
01:44:55,560 --> 01:44:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] premda je kasnije bilo

2444
01:44:57,159 --> 01:45:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] u Mirnodovsku,

2445
01:45:00,119 --> 01:45:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja sam to nosio stalno,

2446
01:45:01,720 --> 01:45:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] do negde,

2447
01:45:02,180 --> 01:45:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] do dve,

2448
01:45:02,840 --> 01:45:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] do dvijet, dvijeljati godine,

2449
01:45:05,319 --> 01:45:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] negde sam nosio,

2450
01:45:06,180 --> 01:45:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] stopstav zapojao sam

2451
01:45:07,380 --> 01:45:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] i pištolji i revolver.

2452
01:45:08,779 --> 01:45:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] A nekima u strahu,

2453
01:45:10,960 --> 01:45:12,939
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosu na tu držku,

2454
01:45:12,939 --> 01:45:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] kao, nažalost,

2455
01:45:14,800 --> 01:45:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] praljak pokojni,

2456
01:45:15,619 --> 01:45:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo se sreli u Zagrebu,

2457
01:45:17,279 --> 01:45:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] nekde on kao,

2458
01:45:17,779 --> 01:45:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] o, di si samoraj,

2459
01:45:18,920 --> 01:45:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] onaki bradak.

2460
01:45:20,159 --> 01:45:21,359
[SPEAKER_00] E, kaže,

2461
01:45:21,359 --> 01:45:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] a di ti ona sablja što si nosio?

2462
01:45:23,779 --> 01:45:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ma kako je sabljistano?

2463
01:45:24,779 --> 01:45:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedino što imam iz kuće,

2464
01:45:27,119 --> 01:45:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari zgrada je komplet izgorila.

2465
01:45:29,920 --> 01:45:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] Svi oni noževi, mačevi, bodježi

2466
01:45:31,840 --> 01:45:32,939
[SPEAKER_00] što sam imao u stanu,

2467
01:45:32,939 --> 01:45:34,560
[SPEAKER_00] u koom malom muzeju,

2468
01:45:34,560 --> 01:45:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] sve to izgorilo.

2469
01:45:35,880 --> 01:45:37,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo moja zgrada,

2470
01:45:37,439 --> 01:45:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] četiri zgrade su gorili od jedan put.

2471
01:45:39,199 --> 01:45:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam uspio ništa,

2472
01:45:40,079 --> 01:45:40,899
[SPEAKER_00] ni iglu sačuvati.

2473
01:45:40,899 --> 01:45:42,979
[SPEAKER_00] Samo taj nož ostao na meni,

2474
01:45:42,979 --> 01:45:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] jel'o, živući.

2475
01:45:43,960 --> 01:45:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u strahu su velike oči.

2476
01:45:46,859 --> 01:45:48,979
[SPEAKER_00] I u odnosu na pogled na držku,

2477
01:45:48,979 --> 01:45:49,479
[SPEAKER_00] on je mislio,

2478
01:45:49,479 --> 01:45:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] to je nekde, ono,

2479
01:45:50,420 --> 01:45:51,659
[SPEAKER_00] sakriveno to,

2480
01:45:53,779 --> 01:45:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] neki su čak umislili,

2481
01:45:55,199 --> 01:45:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] da sam,

2482
01:45:55,779 --> 01:45:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] ti su ti dva noža,

2483
01:45:56,960 --> 01:45:57,260
[SPEAKER_00] sinod,

2484
01:45:57,260 --> 01:45:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] ma nisam nosio dva noža,

2485
01:45:58,539 --> 01:45:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek jedan.

2486
01:45:59,000 --> 01:45:59,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ne, ne,

2487
01:45:59,899 --> 01:46:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] ja,

2488
01:46:00,840 --> 01:46:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] ko,

2489
01:46:01,199 --> 01:46:02,520
[SPEAKER_00] nisam jalo,

2490
01:46:02,520 --> 01:46:03,640
[SPEAKER_00] ako ti malo,

2491
01:46:03,640 --> 01:46:05,060
[SPEAKER_00] znači, bilo je frke.

2492
01:46:05,060 --> 01:46:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali taj nadimak,

2493
01:46:06,199 --> 01:46:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] samura,

2494
01:46:06,579 --> 01:46:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja se ponosim sa tim nadimkom,

2495
01:46:08,380 --> 01:46:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] puno,

2496
01:46:09,420 --> 01:46:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] ni s one strane,

2497
01:46:10,840 --> 01:46:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] a i s ove strane,

2498
01:46:12,619 --> 01:46:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] možda,

2499
01:46:13,119 --> 01:46:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam ime i prezime,

2500
01:46:14,840 --> 01:46:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] desilo se da moj brat poruži u Vrabac,

2501
01:46:17,579 --> 01:46:19,439
[SPEAKER_00] na jednom intervju tu na sajmištu,

2502
01:46:19,439 --> 01:46:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] on kaže,

2503
01:46:20,460 --> 01:46:22,939
[SPEAKER_00] da nije Ivica Dugan došao sa svojim snajperom,

2504
01:46:22,939 --> 01:46:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

2505
01:46:23,239 --> 01:46:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] mi tu dosta popušao.

2506
01:46:24,380 --> 01:46:25,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ja posle njega,

2507
01:46:25,020 --> 01:46:25,560
[SPEAKER_00] ono je,

2508
01:46:25,560 --> 01:46:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] ba ti Lebovo,

2509
01:46:26,500 --> 01:46:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] di si našao Ivica?

2510
01:46:27,239 --> 01:46:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam Antuna,

2511
01:46:28,340 --> 01:46:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] ne Ivica.

2512
01:46:28,819 --> 01:46:29,979
[SPEAKER_00] On koja,

2513
01:46:29,979 --> 01:46:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] ma, znaš,

2514
01:46:30,739 --> 01:46:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

2515
01:46:31,000 --> 01:46:31,479
[SPEAKER_00] ja ovako,

2516
01:46:31,479 --> 01:46:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] onda šuti,

2517
